{"tid":2411734,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警方私家車司機賴錦然衝紅燈撞倒電單車司機 罰款3,000元","createTime":"2021-02-17T14:16:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-17T16:18:12.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"4367c8d55b46d2398f8461ae4f56ed81f64340fb","tid":2411734,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T14:16:33.000Z","msg":"警方私家車前年12月在九龍一個十字路口衝紅燈，與橫過路面的電單車相撞，導致電單車司機受傷。涉案警方私家車司機被控危險駕駛罪，他今在九龍城裁判法院認罪，被判罰款3,000元、停牌6個月兼須參加駕駛改進課程。<br />\n<br />\n案情指被告賴錦然（40歲）於前年12月11日傍晚駕駛警方私家車，沿亞皆老街西行線行駛，至公主道交界時衝紅燈。此時事主李曉波（47歲）在公主道北行線依綠燈指示駕駛電單車，隨即與警方私家車相撞。電單車車頭損毀，私家車則左邊車身損毀。事主意外後自行到醫院求醫，即日出院，獲批四天病假。警方草擬的案情只提及電單車事主經治療後傷勢輕微，沒有詳述傷勢。<br />\n<br />\n約一個月後，被告與警員進行錄影會面，警誡下他稱當時現場的兩組交通燈，分別顯示為黃燈及紅燈，但他以為紅燈交通燈與黃燈那組是同一組燈，故此繼續駛前；但實情是該路口正準備轉紅燈。被告續稱：「之後被電單車撞到左邊後，我停車，落車後先見到路口有兩組燈。我應該要喺第二組燈（按：即紅燈）度停車。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210217/3QINWYEEBVE4JDIWGTFPLJSXTY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210217%2F3QINWYEEBVE4JDIWGTFPLJSXTY%2F&d=bV20Ktv%2Bt3m81RcJrVEN2%2F3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=89e59d94\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210217%2F3QINWYEEBVE4JDIWGTFPLJSXTY%2F&h=3d0b03df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210217/3QINWYEEBVE4JDIWGTFPLJSXTY/</a>"},{"pid":"1c7c16416e9167f035768858231ee31fffc925d0","tid":2411734,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T14:17:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"212cdf84614f53d7c3d4801b2a2360bb9bdb0bbe","tid":2411734,"uid":123774,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T14:20:14.000Z","msg":"黑警又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港市民條命賤過地底黎"},{"pid":"f744935e0200cc25de87b94410cd912102da2569","tid":2411734,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T14:21:17.000Z","msg":"好癲"},{"pid":"0eca84d070a17974e3b572746b6656faddbb5b7f","tid":2411734,"uid":115579,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T14:22:41.000Z","msg":"警員執勤有壓力，撞到人代表平時工作辛苦，本席理應先贊揚被告情操高尚，而呢件事係一件不幸嘅事件，判處象徵性罰款"},{"pid":"e6883cb9116521bc3f16dfe4f1859f8da754e97a","tid":2411734,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T14:22:49.000Z","msg":"天龍人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0a78cbbeaaa3dfedeafaa2a33656879a6fef062","tid":2411734,"uid":45123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T14:23:26.000Z","msg":"法治笑話又多一單"},{"pid":"874b05d51409e8696756b6936b10c48f6f15b0de","tid":2411734,"uid":178459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T14:23:36.000Z","msg":"721 831<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0114424418e88dff1e8ffe0459dccc4aebe7a2e5","tid":2411734,"uid":138964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T14:25:18.000Z","msg":"被告：你唔起身 我就打到你彈起身<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n起到身即係無事 無事就私下搞掂"},{"pid":"bd615a6ce8756e7576934bc6d4122300ad457768","tid":2411734,"uid":95577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T14:28:34.000Z","msg":"黑警自己寫案情話事主受傷輕微<br />\n又認罪，根本玩哂<br />\n可能事主骨折都唔定<br />\n唔洗上庭任佢噏<br />\n法庭見案情輕微就輕判"},{"pid":"4b161ba57a647b8095c12eaa894a430118279b0b","tid":2411734,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T14:29:53.000Z","msg":"香港法治係笑話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac20cd202508fdbcaad4db9ce03bf10e062ee720","tid":2411734,"uid":256215,"li